REM Title: Exercise2-2
REM Author: Jicxer
REM Target: Windows11
REM Description:Exercise2-2
REM Modify payload from Exercise2-1 to pause between the text "Hello," and "World!" until the button is pressed.
DELAY 1000
WINDOWS r
STRING notepad
DELAY 1000
ENTER
DELAY 1000
BUTTON_DEF
    STRING Hello,
    BUTTON_DEF
        STRING World!
        ENTER
        STRING End of exercise2-2
    END_BUTTON
END_BUTTON
